│ is in a block that dominates all subsequent uses produced by the builder. SLP │
│ is doing 'lazy' shuffle emission and mixes the creation of subvector inserts  │
│ and shuffles across the reconstruction of a vector value from multiple lanes, │
│ sometimes reusing 'Root' and then merging shuffles                            │
│ (ShuffleInstructionBuilder). When subvector indices align, createInsertVector │
│ chooses the intrinsic path unconditionally. However, because SLP is           │
