│ required. It                                                                  │
│ 16136 /// supports shuffling of 2 input vectors. It implements lazy shuffles  │
│ emission,                                                                     │
│ 16137 /// when the actual shuffle instruction is generated only if this is    │
│ actually                                                                      │
│ 16138 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed    │
│ till the                                                                      │
│ 16139 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions    │
│ and further                                                                   │
│ 16140 /// analysis/transformations.                                           │
│ 16141 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle     │
│ instructions                                                                  │
│ 16142 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                         │
│ 16143 /// For example, given the code                                         │
│ 16144 /// \code                                                               │
