│ 16146 /// Merges shuffle masks and emits final shuffle instruction, if        │
│ required. It                                                                  │
│ 16147 /// supports shuffling of 2 input vectors. It implements lazy shuffles  │
│ emission,                                                                     │
│ 16148 /// when the actual shuffle instruction is generated only if this is    │
│ actually                                                                      │
│ 16149 /// required. Otherwise, the shuffle instruction emission is delayed    │
│ till the                                                                      │
│ 16150 /// end of the process, to reduce the number of emitted instructions    │
│ and further                                                                   │
│ 16151 /// analysis/transformations.                                           │
│ 16152 /// The class also will look through the previously emitted shuffle     │
│ instructions                                                                  │
│ 16153 /// and properly mark indices in mask as undef.                         │
│ 16154 /// For example, given the code                                         │
│ 16155 /// \code                                                               │
│ 16156 /// %s1 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %0, poison, <1, 0>                     │
│ 16157 /// %s2 = shufflevector <2 x ty> %1, poison, <1, 0>                     │
